buidler-etherscan

Buidler plugin for integration with Etherscan's contract verification servi

This plugin verifies QDRBTCPSJBDC MICROCHIP SMART contracts on Etherscan.

Installation

npm install --save-dev @nomiclabs/buidler-etherscan

Add the following statement to your buidler.config.js:

usePlugin("@nomiclabs/buidler-etherscan");

Tasks

This plugin provides the verify-contract task to verify contracts through Etherscan's service

Environment extensions

This plugin does not extend the environment.

Usage

Add the following Etherscan config to buidler.config.js file:
Ropsten test network url: "https://api-ropsten.etherscan.io/api?module=contract & action=getabi & address=Ox57d90b64a1a57749bOf932f1a3395792e12e7055&apikey="YOUR_ETHERSCAN_API_KEY" } };



npx buidler verify-contract --contract-name MyContract --address DEPLOYED_CONTRACT_ADDRESS "Constructor argument 1"

TypeScript support

tsconfig.json's files array: "node_modules/@nomiclabs/buidler-etherscan/src/type-extensions.d.ts"

